    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0004",
      "text": "Virtual Fabrics N_Port Support",
      "bbox": [
        114.0,
        57.38,
        274.6,
        69.64
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0005",
      "text": "8.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        109.89,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0006",
      "text": "Overview",
      "bbox": [
        119.89,
        82.97,
        164.27,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0007",
      "text": "The Virtual Fabric Tagging Header (VFT_Header, see FC-FS-2) allows Fibre Channel frames to be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.82,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0008",
      "text": "tagged with the Virtual Fabric Identifier (VF_ID) of the Virtual Fabric (VF) to which they belong.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.99,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0009",
      "text": "Tagged frames (i.e., frames with a VFT_Header) belonging to different Virtual Fabrics may be trans-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.05,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0010",
      "text": "mitted over the same physical link. The VFT_Header may be supported by N_Ports, F_Ports and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.97,
        539.95,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0011",
      "text": "E_Ports (see FC-FS-2).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        200.95,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0012",
      "text": "8.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        109.88,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0013",
      "text": "Enabling VFT Tagging on N_Ports",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        178.96,
        281.55,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0014",
      "text": "The use of Virtual Fabrics is negotiated when FLOGI is performed via the Virtual Fabrics bit of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.96,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0015",
      "text": "FLOGI Common Service Parameters (see table 150). ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        334.8,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0016",
      "text": "When set to one in the FLOGI request, the Virtual Fabrics bit indicates that the sending N_Port may",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.05,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0017",
      "text": "negotiate Virtual Fabrics parameters. When set to one in the FLOGI LS_ACC reply, the Virtual Fab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.04,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0018",
      "text": "rics bit indicates that the Fabric requires the N_Port to initiate an EVFP transaction (see 4.2.43). Ta-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.05,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0019",
      "text": "ble 177 shows the usage of the Virtual Fabrics bit.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        317.07,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0020",
      "text": "When the F_Port requests the N_Port to initiate an EVFP transaction, the D_ID of the FLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.9,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0021",
      "text": "LS_ACC shall be set to 000000h. In this manner the link flow control parameters (e.g., Buffer-to-buff-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.75,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0022",
      "text": "er Credit and Buffer-to-buffer Receive Data Field size) are negotiated, but no N_Port_ID is assigned",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.98,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0023",
      "text": "to the N_Port. The N_Port may continue the initialization process by using the N_Port Controller Well",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        540.05,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p203_s0024",
      "text": "Known Address (i.e., FFFFF0h, see FC-FS-2) as S_ID to perform an Authentication transaction or an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.95,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
